title: Stormzy, Dua Lipa win big at star-studded BRIT awards
text:
Stormzy, Dua Lipa win big at star-studded BRIT awards Thursday, February 22, 2018 - 00:51 
British artists Stormzy and Dua Lipa both took two trophies at the prestigious BRIT music awards that featured performances from some of the biggest names in pop. Rough cut (no reporter narration).
